  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/04e370c417f239746b12a2ca9347da19.poster.avif?t=1718870971\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/04e370c417f239746b12a2ca9347da19.webm?t=1718870971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/04e370c417f239746b12a2ca9347da19.mp4?t=1718870971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You're a rookie firefighter battling blazes around town... the perfect cover to steal valuable loot.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Use a variety of water sources to tackle the fire, with limited water and hose lengths.<br></li><li> Rescue citizens trapped by the fire.<br></li><li> Attempt to steal special items on each map without letting the fire get out of control.<br></li><li> Purposely spread the fire to distract and destroy.<br></li><li> Avoid police and other firefighters as you escape with the loot.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Bring On The Water</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/fc0ce36a649a51b5e5a003e978e583b5.poster.avif?t=1718870971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/fc0ce36a649a51b5e5a003e978e583b5.webm?t=1718870971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/fc0ce36a649a51b5e5a003e978e583b5.mp4?t=1718870971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Grab a hose from any fire truck or fire hydrant.<br></li><li> Watch you don't wrap your hose around too many objects or the hose will feel a lot shorter than it is.<br></li><li> Vary your water pressure to arc the stream over objects.<br></li><li> Choose when to use precious water and when to let things burn.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Flame or Fortune?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/3793633696ffd6be4ecda277e5f19504.poster.avif?t=1718870971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/3793633696ffd6be4ecda277e5f19504.webm?t=1718870971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/3793633696ffd6be4ecda277e5f19504.mp4?t=1718870971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Each level has five objects to steal and sell.<br></li><li> Some loot can only be reached by first burning objects in the way.<br></li><li> You have no pockets. Just two hands and room on your back.<br></li><li> Heavy loot will remove your ability to jump over obstacles.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Hero and Villain</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/42782e4db6955b386dedf6dca15aeddd.poster.avif?t=1718870971\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/42782e4db6955b386dedf6dca15aeddd.webm?t=1718870971\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2762330/extras/42782e4db6955b386dedf6dca15aeddd.mp4?t=1718870971\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Once loot is stolen all police and firefighters will be hostile until you can sell it.<br></li><li> The fire can be harnessed to create distractions and burn a path out of danger.</li></ul>",
